{
  "texts": [
    "Prompts were organised into three components: base (context and goal setting), template (content and structure), and style (formatting).",
    "Experiment 3 was a customisation experiment to test a new prompt structure (base, template, style preferences) for generating custom notes based on a transcript.",
    "Experiment 7 introduced a first-person perspective in generated notes.",
    "Experiment 8 refined the style section by incorporating negations and an \"unknown\" category for problems not explicitly mentioned in transcripts.",
    "Experiment 4 tested an enhancement to the baseline SOAP (Subjective, Objective, Assessment, Plan) note by improving medication record representation."
  ]
}